22
00:00:38,630 --> 00:00:41,592
mas adoraria
se vocês fossem.

23
00:00:41,675 --> 00:00:42,843
Sim, claro.

24
00:00:43,844 --> 00:00:45,512
Tchau! (risos)

25
00:00:47,348 --> 00:00:48,349
Tchau.

26
00:00:49,475 --> 00:00:52,519
ANYA:
Então, parece que ela superou
qualquer constrangimento.

27
